KURTZLEBEN: (Laughter).
KEITH: ...Where he was trying to say that he can be electable. And it was an electability argument.
KURTZLEBEN: Sure.
KEITH: And then Senator Amy Klobuchar jumps in.
(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED RECORDING)
